quran[7{c,v,t}:
24,37,unn mein aisay log subah o shaam uss ki tasbeeh karte hain jinhein tijarat aur khareed o farokht Allah ki yaad se aur Iqamat namaz o adaye zkoh se ghaafil nahi kar deti woh uss din se drtay rehtay hain jis mein dil ulatnay aur daiday pathra jaane ki nobat aa jaye gi
24,38,"( aur woh yeh sab kuch is liye karte hain ) taakay Allah un ke behtareen aamaal ki jaza unn ko day aur mazeed apne fazl se nawaze, Allah jisay chahta hai be hisaab deta hai"
24,39,"( is ke bar aks ) jinhon ne kufar kya un ke aamaal ki misaal aisi hai jaisay dasht be aabb mein saraab ke piyasa uss ko pani samjhay hue tha, magar jab wahan pouncha to kuch nah paaya, balkay wahan is ne Allah ko mojood paaya, jis ne is ka poora poora hisaab chuka diya, aur Allah ko hisaab letay der nahi lagti"
24,40,"ya phir is ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik gehray samandar mein andhera, ke oopar aik mouj chhai hui hai, uss par aik aur mouj, aur is ke oopar baadal, tareqi par tareqi musallat hai, aadmi apna haath nikalay to usay bhi nah dekhnay paye jisay Allah noor nah bakhshay uss ke liye phir koi noor nahi"
24,41,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah ki tasbeeh kar rahay hain woh sab jo asmano aur zameen mein hain aur woh parinday jo par phela ye urr rahay hain? har aik apni namaz aur tasbeeh ka tareeqa jaanta hai, aur yeh sab jo kuch karte hain Allah is se bakhabar rehta hai"
24,42,asmano aur zameen ki badshahi Allah hi ke liye hai aur isi ki taraf sab ko palatna hai
24,43,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah baadal ko aahista aahista chalata hai, phir is ke tukron ko baahum jorta hai, phir usay samaitt kar aik kaseef abr bana deta hai, phir tum dekhte ho ke is ke khoal mein se barish ke qatray tpkte chalay atay hain aur woh aasman se, unn pahoron ki badolat jo is mein buland hain, olley barsata hai, phir jisay chahta hai un ka nuqsaan pohanchata hai aur jisay chahta hai un se bacha laita hai uss ki bijli ki chamak nigahon ko Khaira kiye deti hai"
